<topic template="Default" modified="2026-06-14T21:51:55.732Z" lasteditedby="tim" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>Loading Firmware</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>current directory</keyword>
    <keyword>ds10_v7_3.exe</keyword>
    <keyword>firmware</keyword>
    <keyword>--firmware</keyword>
    <keyword>ini default</keyword>
    <keyword>SRM image</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Loading Firmware</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Pass the SRM image explicitly so the path resolves regardless of the ini default:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">--firmware firmware/ds10_v7_3.exe</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Relying on the ini fallback resolves the bare name <text styleclass="Code Example">ds10_v7_3.exe</text> against the current directory, so an explicit <text styleclass="Code Example">--firmware</text> is the reliable form. See Firmware Requirements for selection precedence and the optional SHA-256 integrity check.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See Also.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="--Firmware-Requirements">Firmware Requirements</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="--Reaching-the-SRM-Prompt">Reaching the SRM Prompt</link></para>
  </body>
</topic>
